---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<Layout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<main>
		<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
				<h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Do you love Korea? If so, you'll want to pay attention.</h2>
		</div>

		<h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
				What if the toothbrush, detergent, and cosmetics you use every day started paying you a salary?
		</h1>

		<p>From the moment you open your eyes in the morning until you fall asleep at night, you are consuming. It's a lifelong cycle. Have you ever stopped to consider if there's a better, smarter way to do it?</p>

		<blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid #ccc; padding-left: 1rem; margin-left: 0; font-style: italic;">
				"I can't use anything else."<br>
				"I've been using only this for over 10 years."
		</blockquote>

		<p>Without a single ad or fancy packaging, some people remain loyal to one product for over a decade or two. What does this phenomenon, created voluntarily by some of the world's most discerning consumers in Korea, truly signify?</p>

		<h3 style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 2rem;">KoctoGame begins with this 'real experience'.</h3>

		<p>We are not asking you to buy something new. Instead, we propose a way to transform your existing daily expenses into your <strong>smartest source of income</strong>.</p>

