				<li><strong>A Difference in Quality:</strong> An unparalleled product performance that makes you forget all others after a single use.</li>
				<li><strong>A Difference in Benefits:</strong> The distribution profits that once went to sellers are now returned directly to you, the consumer.</li>
				<li><strong>A Difference in Opportunity:</strong> A new possibility that begins simply by sharing a great product you've experienced first-hand.</li>
		</ul>

		<p>This isn't a story you've never heard before. It's the most common-sense story of changing the paradigm of consumption that was already in your bathroom, your kitchen, and on your vanity.</p>

		<h3 style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center;">Curious how your daily consumption can become your income?</h3>

		<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
				<a href="https://www.koctogame.com/about/" style="text-decoration: none; background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 10px;">Learn About Our Philosophy</a>
				<a href="https://www.koctogame.com/blog/" style="text-decoration: none; background-color: #6c757d; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Become the Smartest Consumer</a>
		</div>

	</main>
</Layout>